{"tid":1393552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！721元朗區議會開特別會議被反對！！竟然冇人講！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:50:01.000Z","uid":252151,"like":329,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"95936ff2282bb2b894d15be4cd6d8ebcbeb7d698","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"小妹住元朗，岩岩去左搵元朗區一位議員問下有冇最新情況！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來一班泛民既元朗區議員想召開<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">特別會議討論721事件</span></span>，迫警方表態！！！但個會尋日竟然趁八號風球打風截左止！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVBKAVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVBKAVu.jpg&h=564d6321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">據說得35個議員回覆，大比數人反對！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lpjgr2y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpjgr2y.jpg&h=7ee89e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員同我講，暫時已知只有泛民既麥議員、黃議員、鄺議員、陳議員、杜議員，五位議員係贊成票，可能有其他少數議員投，但不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結果個會會拖到9月先開！！！<br />\n大家接受到只係拘捕12個白衣人，721件事就咁完左？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗區居民要迫元朗區議員理依件事！！<br />\n應該所有議員都要表態投咩票！！<br />\n證明元朗既區議員大部分都失職，至元朗居民安全於不顧！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家要一齊發聲<br />\n元朗區居民快啲做下野<br />\n特別係yoho一帶</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e606b6340ba64f5ae8b8dcc0d4b0aff1136e5dc4","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"957ac13b0b803d67d790550d6bb656e458e51a01","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"20618a11db08829c84f007933efd40f3184875d3","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"c57e60e4dfed6e17b3a8823cbb1807ee50cc9cda","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"2c6e276db202a29123b6e95413da25d956801002","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"50b4cc757a02d64f99f1ba5790b2510bd34c46b1","tid":1393552,"uid":88675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"我要8月5罷工"},{"pid":"3ee9a1ec557c1ea428619f2149c4677cef3891a9","tid":1393552,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"455ebea52ce925f89e10a443e646dce68bee95a7","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"d200b1648103249381412a0e0a899c5da9691045","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"0bfed543a6075989c25087be54d7cd625b14b97f","tid":1393552,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"置頂置頂"},{"pid":"d4e06b