replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"就算議席唔夠，日日去西鐵站派傳傳單話邊個邊個反對調查，與警同行默許721白衫恐襲<br />\n<br />\n都夠民意逼佢支持啦"},{"pid":"fbf065f9db5c31ca049190dcba641e035097bb4c","tid":1393552,"uid":65184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"第一次「請你出示委任證」被拒的話，應警告佢「拒絕的話，會懷疑你冒警，會請身邊朋友開live，將來你所講嘅每一句都會作為呈堂證供」。<br />\n<br />\n第二步，繼續請佢出示委任證，拒絕的話，俾多兩次機會佢，根據警察通例，（一）便衣人員與巿民接觸時，不論是否當值，在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。(PGO 20-16)」。<br />\n<br />\n三次請求都被拒絕嘅話，可向有證警官報警，懷疑有人冒警。<br />\n如果警官代為出示委任證的話，就話仍然要求該名警員出示委任證，你要紀錄並保留日後向監警會進行投訴嘅權利（視乎該名警員有啲咩唔恰當嘅地方）。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b69ba699f866d0c4c87bde8dbcecb6a76a5537","tid":1393552,"uid":93161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"區選元天人真係要合力踢走班鄉黑牛屎佬"},{"pid":"2e81abb30dbe77d8397f66efa3453c02d1df0f77","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"b9403f7964aa6d5c5eac7d86ea3ad30eae410b6b","tid":1393552,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"cc273b5d9092608391fdd7d0bbcf0333e2a29584","tid":1393552,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa51a73782201a35d788e5932878ea974516871f","tid":1393552,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"極黑暗"},{"pid":"075338b26dae290f60613b1b8b61ad6f00a7c83d","tid":1393552,"uid":65184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"並肩作戰，我要罷工"},{"pid":"0be9cbe01f3733ad2ff03b7227a8b3cc7152ea03","tid":1393552,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":