"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"小妹住元朗，岩岩去左搵元朗區一位議員問下有冇最新情況！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來一班泛民既元朗區議員想召開<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">特別會議討論721事件</span></span>，迫警方表態！！！但個會尋日竟然趁八號風球打風截左止！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVBKAVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVBKAVu.jpg&h=564d6321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">據說得35個議員回覆，大比數人反對！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lpjgr2y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpjgr2y.jpg&h=7ee89e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員同我講，暫時已知只有泛民既麥議員、黃議員、鄺議員、陳議員、杜議員，五位議員係贊成票，可能有其他少數議員投，但不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結果個會會拖到9月先開！！！<br />\n大家接受到只係拘捕12個白衣人，721件事就咁完左？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗區居民要迫元朗區議員理依件事！！<br />\n應該所有議員都要表態投咩票！！<br />\n證明元朗既區議員大部分都失職，至元朗居民安全於不顧！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家要一齊發聲<br />\n元朗區居民快啲做下野<br />\n特別係yoho一帶</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:22:20.000Z"